# Sprint Plan

## Sprint Goal

Develop a Minimum Viable Product (MVP) that allows students to register, log in, and manage assignments.



## Selected User Stories

* US-001 Register account
* US-002 Login
* US-003 Add assignment
* US-006 View assignments
* US-007 Receive reminders



